### Use **/ in the beginning. Otherwise .gitignore cannot recognize the files/folders. ###

# Unity generated folders
**/[Ll]ibrary/
**/[Tt]emp/
**/[Oo]bj/
**/[Bb]uild/
**/[Bb]uilds/
**/[Ll]ogs/
**/[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/

# MemoryCaptures can get excessive in size, also could contain extremely sensitive data
**/[Mm]emoryCaptures/

# Asset meta data should only be ignored when the corresponding asset is also ignored
!**/[Aa]ssets/**/*.meta

# Uncomment this line if you wish to ignore the asset store tools plugin
# **/Assets/AssetStoreTools*

# EditorUserSettings easily creates merge conflict but is only needed locally
**\UserSettings\EditorUserSettings.asset

# Ignore certain Unity asset files
**/Assets/stats.txt
**/Assets/score_screenshot.jpg
**/Assets/BuildReports/
# Keep important assets (remove these if necessary)
# **/Assets/SimpleHands/Materials/White-Hand.mat*

# Recordings can get excessive in size
**/[Rr]ecordings/

# User-specific settings and logs
**/[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/

# Visual Studio and Rider directories
**/.vs/
**/.idea/
**/.gradle/

# Autogenerated Jetbrains Rider plugin
**/Assets/Plugins/Editor/JetBrains*

# Autogenerated Visual Studio/MonoDevelop/Consulo project files
**/ExportedObj/
**/.consulo/
**/*.csproj
**/*.unityproj
**/*.sln
**/*.suo
**/*.tmp
**/*.user
**/*.userprefs
**/*.pidb
**/*.booproj
**/*.svd
**/*.pdb
**/*.mdb
**/*.opendb
**/*.VC.db
**/*.log

# Unity3D generated meta files
**/*.pidb.meta
**/*.pdb.meta
**/*.mdb.meta

# Unity3D generated file on crash reports
**/sysinfo.txt

# Builds
**/*.apk
**/*.aab
**/*.unitypackage
**/*.app

# Crashlytics generated file
**/crashlytics-build.properties

# Packed Addressables
**/Assets/AddressableAssetsData/*/*.bin*
**/Assets/AddressableAssetsData/link.xml*
**/Assets/AddressableAssetsData/Windows.meta

# Temporary auto-generated Android Assets
**/Assets/StreamingAssets/aa.meta
**/Assets/StreamingAssets/aa/*

# macOS Specific
**/.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store?
**/._*
**/.Spotlight-V100
**/.Trashes
**/ehthumbs.db
**/Thumbs.db
**/report.xml
**/Thumbs.db.meta

# Response files (generated during the build process)
**/*.rsp
**/*.rsp.meta

# VRManifest
**/unityProject.vrmanifest

# Photoshop files (remove if needed)
**/*.psd

# Unity3D Layouts
**/Logs/
**/UserSettings/Layouts/default-2021.dwlt

# Asset Hunter build info
**/*.ahbuildinfo

# FMOD logs and cache files
**/fmod.log
**/fmod_editor.log
**/Assets/Plugins/FMOD/Cache/Editor/FMODStudioCache.asset
**/Assets/Plugins/FMOD/Cache/Editor/FMODStudioCache.asset.meta
**/Assets/Plugins/FMOD/Cache/Editor.meta

# VS Code settings folder
**/.vscode/

# Deployment logs
**/Deploy/*.log

# Temporary files
**/temp/
